=== 宿舍 ===
[[File:Erdman_Bryn_Mawr.JPG|thumb]]
該學院的大部分學生住在宿舍裡，很多古老的學生宿舍由原來的科普和史都華德遜（Cope & Stewardson）設計，以其仿照[[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]]的[[學院哥特式|學院哥特式]]風格著稱。其名稱都是拿[[威爾士|威爾士]]的[[郡治|郡治]]，例如[[布雷肯|布雷肯]]、[[登比|登比]]、[[梅里恩|梅里恩]]、[[新拉德諾|拉德諾]]等命名的。此外也有拿第一任校長羅茲的名字來命名的宿舍。最新的宿舍是[[路易·卡恩|路易·卡恩]]設計、在1965年啟用的現代主義風格埃德曼堂（Erdman Hall）<ref>{{cite journal |work=The Architecture Week's Great Building Collection |url=http://www.greatbuildings.com/buildings/Erdman_Hall_Dormitories.html |title=Erdman Hall Dormitories |journal= |access-date=2015-01-16 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221185911/http://greatbuildings.com/buildings/Erdman_Hall_Dormitories.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 及1971年啟用的哈夫納語言文化宅（Haffner Language and Culture House）。<ref>[http://www.saveardmorecoalition.org/node/1694 Glenmede Saved From Destruction and Over-Development] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120912180526/http://www.saveardmorecoalition.org/node/1694 |date=2012年9月12日 }}. Save Ardmore Coalition (2005-10-13). Retrieved on 2011-06-18.</ref>

=== 圖書館===
[[File:Carey_Thomas_from_S.jpg|thumb]]
布林莫爾學院的圖書館包括1970年啟用的瑪利亞姆·科菲·卡納迪圖書館（Mariam Coffin Canaday Library）、1993年啟用的路易和雷金納德·科利爾圖書館（Lois and Reginald Collier Science Library）及1997年啟用的里斯·卡彭特圖書館（Rhys Carpenter Library）。<ref name="autogenerated1" /><ref>[http://www.brynmawr.edu/visit/guided_tour/carpenter.shtml Bryn Mawr College | Visiting Campus] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071105230332/http://www.brynmawr.edu/visit/guided_tour/carpenter.shtml |date=2007-11-05 }}. Brynmawr.edu. Retrieved on 2011-06-18.</ref>

M·凱利·托馬斯圖書館（M. Carey Thomas Library）以該校第二任校長的名字命名，直到1970年為止都是該校的主圖書館，現在也仍然可以使用。該圖書館的中庭叫做“The Cloisters”，是舉行該校傳統燈火晚會的地方。凱利·托馬斯和[[埃米·諾特|埃米·諾特]]的墓地也在此處。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Mann|first1=Janice|title=Women Medievalists and the Academy|date=2005|publisher=University of Wisconsin Press|page=121}}</ref> 這座建築在1991年選為[[美國國家歷史名勝|美國國家歷史名勝]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tps.cr.nps.gov/nhl/detail.cfm?ResourceId=2117&ResourceType=Building |title=M. Carey Thomas Library |accessdate=2008-02-11 |work=National Historic Landmark summary listing |publisher=National Park Service |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606111044/http://tps.cr.nps.gov/nhl/detail.cfm?ResourceId=2117&ResourceType=Building |archivedate=2011-06-06 }}</ref><ref name="nrhpinv2">{{Cite journal|title=Photos from 1936, 1980, 1983, and undated, to accompany National Register of Historic Places Inventory-Nomination: M. Carey Thomas Library (text not available)|url=http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Photos/91002052.pdf|format=pdf|date=|author=|publisher=National Park Service|journal=|access-date=2015-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120821235627/http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Photos/91002052.pdf|archive-date=2012-08-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 劇院 ===

學院裡的馬喬里·沃爾特·古德哈特劇院（Marjorie Walter Goodhart Theater）由美國建築師[[亞瑟·英格索爾·梅格斯|亞瑟·英格索爾·梅格斯]]設計，用作藝術表演和排練之用。劇院的[[哥特復興式|哥特復興式]]高塔則是由[[薩繆爾·耶林|薩繆爾·耶林]]設計的。<ref>[http://www.brynmawr.edu/visit/guided_tour/goodhart.shtml Bryn Mawr College | Visiting Campus] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071105230340/http://www.brynmawr.edu/visit/guided_tour/goodhart.shtml |date=2007-11-05 }}. Brynmawr.edu. Retrieved on 2011-06-18.</ref><ref name="autogenerated1">[http://www.lowermerionhistory.org/texts/first300/part18.html The First 300: The Amazing and Rich History of Lower Merion (Part 18)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lowermerionhistory.org/texts/first300/part18.html |date=20200224045213 }}. Lowermerionhistory.org. Retrieved on 2011-06-18.</ref> 2009年秋學院投資1900萬美金對這座劇院進行了翻修。<ref>[http://news.brynmawr.edu/?p=3959 Bryn Mawr Now: To Inaugurate a Reconceived Goodhart, Bi-College Theater Production Probes Language, Space] {{Wayback|url=http://news.brynmawr.edu/?p=3959 |date=20110722010253 }}  Retrieved April 27, 2010</ref>

