布林莫爾學院是一座小型的四年制學院，<ref name="Carnegie">{{cite web |url=http://www.carnegiefoundation.org/classifications/sub.asp?key=748&subkey=15920&start=782 |title=Bryn Mawr College – Carnegie Classifications |publisher=Carnegie Foundation for the Advancement of Teaching |accessdate=2009-05-30}}</ref> 雖然也提供研究生課程，但絕大多數學生都是本科生。<ref name="CDS">{{cite web|url=http://www.brynmawr.edu/institutionalresearch/documents/CDS2009_2010.pdf |title=Common Data Set 2009-2009 |publisher=Bryn Mawr College |accessdate=2009-05-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100408162134/http://www.brynmawr.edu/institutionalresearch/documents/CDS2009_2010.pdf |archivedate=2010-04-08 }}</ref> 2019年排在《[[美國新聞和世界報道|美國新聞和世界報道]]》“全國最佳文理學院”中的第27位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/bryn-mawr-college-211273/overall-rankings|title=Bryn Mawr College|publisher=U.S. News|accessdate=2018-12-16|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100352/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/bryn-mawr-college-211273/overall-rankings|dead-url=no}}</ref>

學院科目劃分為人文、社會科學和自然科學三類，學生必須要完成一年的外語課程、習得一門定量技巧，并完成新生寫作課艾米麗·鮑爾奇研討會（Emily Balch Seminars）。<ref>{{cite web|title=The Emily Balch Seminars|url=http://www.brynmawr.edu/balch/|work=Bryn Mawr College Undergraduate Courses|publisher=Bryn Mawr College|accessdate=2 March 2011|archive-date=2014-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702234631/http://www.brynmawr.edu/balch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年布林莫爾學院共收到2,276份申請，批准了其中的1107（48.6%）份，最終有362（32.7%）人入學。新生[[SAT|SAT]]成績閱讀為600–700、數學為580–680 、寫作為620–700。<ref name="CDS"/> 四年之後的畢業率為81.4%。<ref name="CDS"/>

== 傳統==
[[Image:BMCMayDay.jpg|thumb]]
布林茅爾學院有四項主要傳統獲得，即每學年開始舉辦的遊行晚會（Parade Night）、十月末十一月初舉辦的燈火晚會、二月中旬舉辦的地獄周（Hell Week）以及春季學期結束後的第一個星期日的[[五朔節|五朔節]]。學生們會選出兩名女性來負責運行這些活動。<ref>{{cite web|title=Student Activities: Traditions|url=http://www.brynmawr.edu/activities/traditions.shtml|work=brynmawr.edu|accessdate=16 March 2011|quote=The Traditions Mistresses, elected officers of the SGA, organize the traditions throughout the academic year.|archive-date=2017-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804101712/http://www.brynmawr.edu/activities/traditions.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.brynmawr.edu/activities/traditions.shtml Bryn Mawr College Student Activities] {{Wayback|url=http://www.brynmawr.edu/activities/traditions.shtml |date=20170804101712 }}. Brynmawr.edu. Retrieved on 2011-06-18.</ref>

